              <ul class="date-check">
              <li class="hd-checkbox">
              <input type="radio" id="solar" name="date" class="checkbox__input hidden" data-checked="n" checked="">
              <label for="solar" class="checkbox__label">양력</label>
              </li>
              <li class="hd-checkbox">
              <input type="radio" id="lunar" name="date" class="checkbox__input hidden" data-checked="n">
              <label for="lunar" class="checkbox__label">음력</label>
              </li>
              </ul>
              </div>
              <ul id="anniversaryListArea" class="box">
              <!-- anniversaryListTemplate -->
              </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="agree-box">
              <div class="hd-checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" id="agree" class="checkbox__input hidden" data-checked="n">
              <label for="agree" class="checkbox__label">개인정보 수집·이용 동의(선택)</label>
              </div>
              <div class="agree-table">
              <table>
              <thead>
              <tr>
              <th>수집·이용 항목</th>
              <th>수집·이용 목적</th>
              <th>보유 및 이용기간</th>
              </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
              <tr>
              <td>기념일(양/음력)</td>
              <td>알림톡 발송</td>
              <td>회원탈퇴시 또는 법정 보유 기간</td>
              </tr>
              </tbody>
              </table>
              <p>※ 개인정보 수집·이용에 동의하셔야 서비스 이용이 가능합니다.</p>
              </div>
              </div>
              </section>
